@startuml
' @id(CMP-ARCH-TRACKING)
' @desc(CMP-ARCH-TRACKING, "The architecture-tracking capability: the .mdd/architecture/ structured spec (components/decisions/constraints.yml), the SeededOnce templates mdd init scaffolds for it, and the agent-facing .mdd/docs/architecture-tracking.md that puts the tracking workflow into every agent's context. The structured diff/history verb (mdd arch) is a planned follow-up; git is the interim diff mechanism.")
' Objective-side component for the architecture-tracking capability (cycle 0028).
title Architecture-tracking component (objective)

component "mdd init\n(scaffolds templates)" as Init
artifact ".mdd/architecture/components.yml" as Comp
artifact ".mdd/architecture/decisions.yml" as Dec
artifact ".mdd/architecture/constraints.yml" as Con
artifact ".mdd/docs/architecture-tracking.md" as Doc
component "/mdd-kickoff" as Kick
component "any agent" as Agent

Init --> Comp : create-if-missing
Init --> Dec : create-if-missing
Init --> Con : create-if-missing
Init --> Doc : regenerable
Kick --> Comp : authors initial spec
Agent --> Dec : append + supersede on change
Agent --> Doc : reads how-to
@enduml
